 girl a 50 cent token and she rolled her eyes and I never seen her again, and this was after tipping her a doller per drink for more than 2 hours! At the tables it was complete opposite they kept my glass full. The waitresses in Magnolias were terrible and all didnt care if you ate there or not. I tried to get a cup of soup to go one nite and they said all they had was styrofoam containers and she wouldnt put soup in it, so then I asked for a steak hogie to go and she said they didnt have hogies. So I showed her on the menu that I just looked at and she said &quot;thats a sub not a hogie&quot;? So I just left cause I was so mad at this point and went to the freemont and got chinese take out. Just to let the ladies know,, A bum attempted to rob me outside on freemont street in front of the fremont hotel and casino, but a bicycle cop seen him in action and arrested him approx. 2 am. This was right in front of four queens also and the casino cop seen this and voluntarily escorted me to my room when I returned to the casino.. For me I will absolutely stay here again , the price was right for what we got and we were very pleased.I do however think next time I visit , I will go with my hubby.	
